### =============================================
### MENU
### =============================================

### Get menu — all 6 prices (public — no auth required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu

###

### =============================================
### SETUP — Login as student (sets studentToken)
### =============================================

### Login as student
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/students/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "marko.markovic",
  "password": "student123"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("studentToken", response.body.token);
%}

###

### =============================================
### STUDENT MENU VIEW
### =============================================

### Get menu for my status — 3 prices only (requires STUDENT token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

###

### =============================================
### SETUP — Login as cook (sets cookToken)
### =============================================

### Login as cook
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bart.smith",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("cookToken", response.body.token);
%}



### =============================================
### UPDATE MENU
### =============================================

### Update all prices (requires COOK or ADMIN token)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cookToken}}

{
  "breakfastPriceBudget": 2.00,
  "lunchPriceBudget": 4.00,
  "dinnerPriceBudget": 3.00,
  "breakfastPriceSelfFinance": 2.50,
  "lunchPriceSelfFinance": 4.80,
  "dinnerPriceSelfFinance": 3.60
}

###

### Update a single price (requires COOK or ADMIN token)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cookToken}}

{
  "lunchPriceBudget": 4.00
}

###

### Update menu — as student, not cook (expects 403)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cookToken}}

{
  "breakfastPriceBudget": 1.00
}